-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-20/marubeni-allies-with-irkutsk-to-expand-russia-energy-business-nikkei-says.html

          
          
             Marubeni Corp. has formed an
alliance with Irkutsk Oil Co. to expand its energy operations in
Russia, Nikkei English News said, without citing anyone.  
 The companies may make synthetic resins from gases produced
from Irkutskâ€™s oil fields, the report said. Marubeni may provide
